{"tid":1002513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警中區被捕　涉去年一宗非禮及遊蕩案","createTime":"2019-01-31T04:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T04:42:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"85767619f70a6367ba7b3b7a6b49a0057d0f64b4","tid":1002513,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190130/s00001/38295ec3aa36c59569f965ec561ef459.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190130%2Fs00001%2F38295ec3aa36c59569f965ec561ef459.jpg&h=597bf25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方今日在中區拘捕一名休班警員，涉嫌與去年一宗非禮及遊蕩案有關。<br />\n<br />\n中區警區重案組人員經深入調查及徵詢法律意見後，今日在中區拘捕一名43歲姓黃男子，涉嫌與去年8月3日一宗在中區奧卑利街發生的非禮及遊蕩案有關。被捕男子已被控以一項非禮罪及一項遊蕩罪，案件明日（31日）在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，定必嚴正處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190130/s00001/1548859454950/%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%B6%89%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%97%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE%E5%8F%8A%E9%81%8A%E8%95%A9%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190130%2Fs00001%2F1548859454950%2F%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%2597%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E5%258F%258A%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%2595%25A9%25E6%25A1%2588&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6m7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=a799638c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190130%2Fs00001%2F1548859454950%2F%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%2597%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%25A6%25A